Carmen Viance https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carmen_Viance 0 Carmen Viance (June 21, 1905 – July, 1985) was a Spanish actress who appeared in twenty films between 1924 and 1943, including the 1927 silent film The Mendez Women.
